 INTRODUCTION
 ------------

 The string class of intuition.library have a bug, we  can't  set  an  entire
 string  of  character  it  only  display  MAX.CHAR. -1. For example, when we
 create a string with 5 max. char. and we want to set ( SetGadgetAttrs.. )  a
 string on it, it will display only the 4 first characters.

 This link-librarie contain 3 hook who repair this BUG !


 FEATURES
 --------

 The librarie contain 3 HOOK: StringHook, StringHookReturn and StringHookCommand.

 They repair the Intuition bug, but they have too.. :


    * StringHook:

        - ALT-CURSOR (UP|DOWN): go to another string (if TABCYCLE-MODE ON).

        - ESC: Deactive the string gadget.



    * StringHookReturn:

        - ALT-CURSOR (UP|DOWN): go to another string (if TABCYCLE-MODE ON).

        - ESC: Deactive the string gadget.

        - RETURN: When you validate a string, it will activate the next string-gadget
         (if TABCYCLE-MODE ON).



    * StringHookCommand:

        - ALT-CURSOR (UP|DOWN): go to another string (if TABCYCLE-MODE ON).

        - ESC:  Deactive  the  string  gadget.

        - When RAMIGA or LAMIGA with a <char>, it will active button who have
          the shortcut: <char> or menu who have the shortcut LAMIGA + <char>.



