 USAGE
 -----

 If you want a string  gadget  with  5  characters,  create  it  with  6  max
 characters,  the  hook  will  stop the edition at MAX - 1 characters also we
 can't enter only 5 characters.

 And affect the hook to your string gadget, it will do something like:

    [....]
    STRINGA_MaxChars,      max + 1,
    STRINGA_EditHook,      (ULONG)&StringHook,
    [....]

    or

    [....]
    STRINGA_MaxChars,      max + 1,
    STRINGA_EditHook,      (ULONG)&StringHookReturn,
    [....]


 For users of the bgui.library, you can use the macro in "NewString_macros.h".


